OL,6,F"Labour will not increase taxes on
OL,7,Fworking people, which is why we will
OL,8,Fnot increase National Insurance, the
OL,9,Fbasic, higher, or additional rates of
OL,10,FIncome Tax, or VAT."
OL,12,FAs you can read, the only reference to
OL,13,F"rates" is in respect of income tax.
OL,14,FIn relation to national insurance (NI)
OL,15,Fand VAT, the manifesto just says those
OL,16,Ftaxes won't be increased.
