OL,3,CIs the treasury hinting at tax rise
OL,4,Cwiggle room?
OL,6,FI am interested in Jones talking about
OL,7,Fnot increasing the "headline rate of
OL,8,FVAT". That is because he may have
OL,9,Finadvertently opened a window on
OL,10,FTreasury thinking about how to raise
OL,11,Fperhaps #20bn or so in the autumn
OL,12,Fbudget that may be needed to fill a
OL,13,Fhole in the public finances, to
OL,14,Frestore Reeves's fiscal rules headroom.
