OL,3,CIs the treasury hinting at tax rise
OL,4,Cwiggle room?
OL,6,FTo be clear, the politics for Starmer
OL,7,Fand Reeves of putting up the price of
OL,8,Ffood and energy when living standards
OL,9,Fremain squeezed would be difficult. It
OL,10,Fwould seem to contradict Labour's
OL,11,Fmanifesto promise not to put up costs
OL,12,Ffor "working people".
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@TO]
